Taita Taveta Senator Dan Mwazo says he will win the governor&rsquo;s seat on August 8. &ldquo;I will be the second governor by August 9 this year. As I speak to you now ,I am talking as your governor. I walk and sleep as your governor,&rdquo; Mwazo told journalists at Galaxy hotel in Voi on Monday. He spoke during the selection of nine board members to oversee Jubilee Party nominations.